00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:26,720
And the other, like, huh?

153
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,140
Caveira doesn't exist in the game.

154
00:06:28,601 --> 00:06:31,384
So you only see one aspect of your game

155
00:06:31,404 --> 00:06:33,466
when you play, when you are engaged with.

156
00:06:33,826 --> 00:06:37,130
So that's why you need to have data to see everything,

157
00:06:37,170 --> 00:06:40,774
basically, to have a 360-degree vision of your game.

158
00:06:41,375 --> 00:06:42,917
So OK, data is important.

