00:12:56,028 --> 00:12:57,670
creating shadow for all the other weapons.

306
00:12:58,310 --> 00:13:00,372
So we decided to change them and to nerf them.

307
00:13:00,833 --> 00:13:02,114
And because of the nature of the game,

308
00:13:02,134 --> 00:13:04,256
defenders were using them the most.

309
00:13:04,276 --> 00:13:08,580
So we anticipated kind of an imbalance on the defense side.

310
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,743
And it happened, and it happened like super badly.

311
00:13:12,243 --> 00:13:12,904
When you look at this,

312
00:13:12,984 --> 00:13:15,326
it was one of the worst balance situation we ever had

313
00:13:15,406 --> 00:13:16,928
in the history of the game at that point.

314
00:13:17,709 --> 00:13:19,490
So here, for example, if you're data driven,

315
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:22,851
you might say, maybe we should reverse this change.

